<view class="page-container index-page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-title">AI专业择校助手</view>
    <view class="hero-description">
      基于公开招生数据、专业方向标签和 AI 解释能力，提供 AI 相关专业参考匹配。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card form-card">
    <view class="section-title">填写基本信息</view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <view class="form-label">所在省份</view>
      <input
        class="form-control"
        value="{{form.province}}"
        data-field="province"
        bindinput="onInput"
        placeholder="请输入省份"
      />
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <view class="form-label">高考分数</view>
      <input
        class="form-control"
        type="number"
        value="{{form.score}}"
        data-field="score"
        bindinput="onInput"
        placeholder="请输入高考分数"
      />
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <view class="form-label">全省位次</view>
      <input
        class="form-control"
        type="number"
        value="{{form.rank}}"
        data-field="rank"
        bindinput="onInput"
        placeholder="请输入全省位次"
      />
      <view class="rank-hint">
        位次越小代表排名越靠前，例如 4000 名优于 40000 名。
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <view class="form-label">科类</view>
      <picker
        mode="selector"
        range="{{subjectTypes}}"
        value="{{subjectTypeIndex}}"
        bindchange="onSubjectTypeChange"
      >
        <view class="form-control picker-control">
          <text>{{form.subject_type}}</text>
          <text class="picker-arrow">›</text>
        </view>
      </picker>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <view class="form-label">目标 AI 方向</view>
      <picker
        mode="selector"
        range="{{targetDirections}}"
        value="{{targetDirectionIndex}}"
        bindchange="onTargetDirectionChange"
      >
        <view class="form-control picker-control">
          <text>{{form.target_direction}}</text>
          <text class="picker-arrow">›</text>
        </view>
      </picker>
    </view>

    <view class="switch-row">
      <view>
        <view class="form-label switch-label">启用 AI 专业解释</view>
        <view class="switch-description">生成更自然的学习与就业方向说明</view>
      </view>
      <switch
        checked="{{form.use_ai}}"
        color="#1769AA"
        bindchange="onUseAIChange"
      />
    </view>
  </view>

  <button
    class="primary-button submit-button"
    loading="{{loading}}"
    disabled="{{loading}}"
    bindtap="submitRecommend"
  >
    {{loading ? '正在生成...' : '生成 AI 专业推荐'}}
  </button>

  <view class="page-tip">
    推荐结果仅作信息参考，请以本省考试院及院校官方发布的信息为准。
  </view>

  <view class="compliance-footer">
    <view class="compliance-title">使用前请了解</view>
    <view class="compliance-links">
      <navigator class="compliance-link" url="/pages/about/about">产品说明</navigator>
      <view class="link-divider"></view>
      <navigator class="compliance-link" url="/pages/disclaimer/disclaimer">免责声明</navigator>
      <view class="link-divider"></view>
      <navigator class="compliance-link" url="/pages/privacy/privacy">隐私说明</navigator>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
